    22‚Üí
    25‚Üí### Major Changes
    26‚Üí
    27‚Üí- [#484](https://github.com/supermacro/neverthrow/pull/484) [`09faf35`](https://github.com/supermacro/neverthrow/commit/09faf35a5ce701ed55b13b82074da9e50050526d) Thanks [@braxtonhall](https://github.com/braxtonhall)! - Allow orElse method to change ok types.
    28‚Üí  This makes the orElse types match the implementation.
    29‚Üí
    30‚Üí  This is a breaking change for the orElse type argument list,
    31‚Üí  as the ok type must now be provided before the err type.
    32‚Üí
    33‚Üí  ```diff
    34‚Üí  - result.orElse<ErrType>(foo)
    35‚Üí  + result.orElse<OkType, ErrType>(foo)
    36‚Üí  ```
    37‚Üí
